		</div>

		<div class="col-lg-6">


		      <h2>Demo database</h2>
		      <p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/demo_db.sql" role="button" target="_blank">Download »</a></p>


		      <h2>Required</h2>
		      <ol>
				<li><b>jQuery</b> v2.0+</li>
				<li><b>Twitter bootstrap</b> v3.2+</li>
				<li><b>jquery.nette.js</b> for reloading snippets: <a href="{$basePath}/js/jquery.nette.js" target="_blank">for example</a></li>
				<li>
					<b>jQuery UI</b> v1.10.3 only for \DataGrid\Grid::enableSorting().
					<br><a href="/js/jquery.ui.js" target="_blank">Download jQuery UI v1.10.3</a>
				</li>
			</ol>
			<p><span class="label label-danger">Important:</span> If use default js and css draw, <b>jQuery and jQuery UI must be loaded in HTML &lt;head&gt;</b> or before include grid component in template.</p>
